4. Develop a LaTeX script to create the Certificate Page of the Report [Use suitable commands to leave the blank spaces for user entry].
The certificate page has been composed using two tex files: Certificate.tex contains the content information and MainCertificateExecute.tex contains the layout setting. Both tex files need to be created.
To obtain output pdf file, execute MainCertificateExecute.tex
Certificate.tex
\thispagestyle{empty}
\setlength{\toptafiddle}{1in}
\setlength{\bottafiddle}{1in}
\vspace*{-0.75in}
\enlargethispage{\toptafiddle}
\begin{center}
\begin{Large}
\textbf{Bapuji Institute of Engineering and Technology} \\
\end{Large}
\begin{Large}
\textbf{Davanagere - 577004}\\
\end{Large}
\vspace{0.2cm}
\begin{figure}[h]
\centering
\includegraphics[height=3cm]{graph1.jpg}
\end{figure}
\begin{Large}
\textbf{Department of Computer Science and Engineering} \\
\end{Large}
\Huge{\textbf{Certificate}}
\end{center}
\begin{large}
This is to certify that the Project Report entitled
\textbf{"TITLE"} is a bonafide work carried out by
\textbf{Student-1(USN)}, \textbf{Student-2(USN)},
\textbf{Student-3(USN)} and \textbf{Student-4(USN)}
in the partial fulfillment of the requirement for the award of the degree of
Bachelor of Engineering in Computer Science and Engineering, Visvesvaraya Technological
University, Belagavi during the year 20XX-XX.
It is certified that all corrections/suggestions indicated for the internal assessment
have been incorporated in the report. The project report has been approved as it satisfies the
academic requirements in respect of project
work prescribed for the Bachelor of Engineering Degree.
\end{large}
